{"balanda":"Ni kakolo wiki","english":"He hugged the child."}
{"balanda":"Ndi kamago","english":"They fought."}
{"balanda":"Ni kavanda wiki","english":"He protected the child."}

{"balanda":"Ni kateta","english":"He fell."}
