{"balanda":"Nguu kavere","english":"The tree darkened."}
{"balanda":"Maraya kadeye","english":"The school developed."}
{"balanda":"Wiki karengo","english":"The child matured."}

{"balanda":"Ni kadho gbi tiyi","english":"He was in the house."}
{"balanda":"Ne kama nde","english":"I did the work."}
{"balanda":"Ne kawala gbi Wau","english":"I lived in Wau."}
{"balanda":"Ne kaduru ngo","english":"I wanted water."}
